title: Lucky fish!

pars: Jay Wall spent time fishing in the Waranga Basin and in the local channels over Christmas while spending some quality time with his Nan and Pop, Graeme and Wendy Wall.
He was lucky (and clever) to catch an 80 cm Murray Cod.
Jay was rapt with his catch, got the photo and released the fi sh back into the water to hopefully breed and improve the local Cod population.
Great to see a young fi sherman returning fish to the water.
